{
  "stem": "14737.3",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where are you drafted?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, I didn't expect anything in this world will happen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And what I just make [INAUDIBLE] to the headquarters.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Finally being there three weeks, in the morning, there's a roll call, a big roll-- They call Schwimmer, Zoltan.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They call me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't know what.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They call me in the office.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we received a discharge for you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Received a discharge for you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I couldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was discharged from labor camp that I'm going to go emigrate [INAUDIBLE] I still have this date of discharge is October 1940.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I'm out of the picture.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm not anymore in labor camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I go back to Budapest, and I have already with me a paper.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My status was-- they didn't write for what.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was dismissed or discharged.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, discharged people from labor camp, there's no such a thing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No such a thing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No one had it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So either I was lucky, but it was not yet a harsh labor camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was-- you know, in the beginning, they didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they discharged me, but I feel myself like a million dollars here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People are looking there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And labor camp power, person, there are doctors, there are lawyers, there are people much more important than I am, and they couldn't realize, but this is the story.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I picked myself up and go back to Budapest now.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can go to live wherever I want.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have a discharge.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It will be honored.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's signed by a big officer.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
